title: Dungeons and Dragons 1st ed. -- Tomb of Horrors, Whiteume, Barri
description:
Again, another torrent I don&#039;t know if anybody wants.  But anyone who played the old Dungeons and Dragons knows that these are the best dungeons ever.  Included in this torrent are:



The Tomb of Horrors

Return to the Tomb of Horrors (includes the module above)

White Plume Mountain

Expedition to the Barrier Peaks

Lost Caverns of Tsjocanth

and, another one I threw in, perhaps the greatest non-TSR dungeon ever -- Tegel Manor.  Tegel Manor was made by Judges Guild and is extremely difficult to find -- it costs like $90 on Ebay.  This is the retooled edition (it&#039;s missing some of the kooky stuff from the first one) but the thought is still there.  It&#039;s still a classic module.

I have all of the AD&D modules I can scan if anyone wants them.  Plus the original books for first edition.  If there is demand.
